	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000982_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">26<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> March </p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My <persName>Dear Doctor</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I shall try 
<lb/>and be with you at 
<lb/>11 A.M. tomorrow<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>You must get a 
<lb/>copper boat for 
<lb/>me. <choice><reg>S</reg><orig>s</orig></choice>imilar to 
<lb/><persName>Burton's.</persName><persName>Lord 
<lb/>Clarendon</persName> is agreeable<reg>.</reg>
<lb/><persName>Sir Roderick</persName> will 
<lb/>mention it to you<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>D Livingstone</persName></p>
			
